FAC is a software packge for the calculation of various atomic processes.

INSTALL:
modify the Makefile according to your system. and type "make". After make,
the Python modules will reside in the subdir python. If you need to put it 
in some other dir, set the INSTDIR variable in the make file, and type  
"make install".

Environment variable:
python interpreter must be in your path. $PYTHONPATH that contains the 
installed module must be setup so that Python can find it. e.g. in csh,
	setenv PYTHONPATH INSTALL_DIR
where INSTALL_DIR is the directory where you installed the package.

Usage:
The module can be called just like any python modules, either from 
interpreter interactively, or pass the script to python. 
e.g., python fe24_level.py,
